. Optimized Approach (Two Pointer â€“ Best for Interview)
ğŸ”¹ Logic

Start pointer i = 0

End pointer j = length-1

Characters compare karo

Agar mismatch â†’ false
--------------

public class PalindromeStringOptimized {
    public static boolean isPalindrome(String str) {

        int i = 0;
        int j = str.length() - 1;

        while (i < j) {
            if (str.charAt(i) != str.charAt(j)) {
                return false;
            }
            i++;
            j--;
        }
        return true;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str = "level";
        System.out.println(isPalindrome(str)); // true
    }
}
Complexity

Time: O(n)

Space: O(1) âœ…

